msgctxt "sn35.135:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:0.2"
msgid "14. Devadahavagga "
msgstr "14. At Devadaha "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 135. Khaṇasutta → saṅgayha (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.135:0.3"
msgid "135. Khaṇasutta "
msgstr "135. Opportunity "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.126, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.1"
msgid "“Lābhā vo, bhikkhave, suladdhaṃ vo, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“You’re fortunate, mendicants, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.2"
msgid "khaṇo vo paṭiladdho brahmacariyavāsāya. "
msgstr "to have the opportunity to live the spiritual life. "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.3"
msgid "Diṭṭhā mayā, bhikkhave, chaphassāyatanikā nāma nirayā. "
msgstr "I’ve seen the hell called ‘the six fields of contact’. "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.4"
msgid "Tattha yaṃ kiñci cakkhunā rūpaṃ passati aniṭṭharūpaṃyeva passati, no iṭṭharūpaṃ; akantarūpaṃyeva passati, no kantarūpaṃ; amanāparūpaṃyeva passati, no manāparūpaṃ. "
msgstr "There, whatever sight you see with your eye is unlikable, not likable; undesirable, not desirable; unpleasant, not pleasant. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.5"
msgid "Yaṃ kiñci sotena saddaṃ suṇāti … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever sound you hear … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.6"
msgid "yaṃ kiñci ghānena gandhaṃ ghāyati … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever odor you smell … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.7"
msgid "yaṃ kiñci jivhāya rasaṃ sāyati … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever flavor you taste … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.8"
msgid "yaṃ kiñci kāyena phoṭṭhabbaṃ phusati … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever touch you feel … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.9"
msgid "yaṃ kiñci manasā dhammaṃ vijānāti aniṭṭharūpaṃyeva vijānāti, no iṭṭharūpaṃ; akantarūpaṃyeva vijānāti, no kantarūpaṃ; amanāparūpaṃyeva vijānāti, no manāparūpaṃ. "
msgstr "Whatever thought you know with your mind is unlikable, not likable; undesirable, not desirable; unpleasant, not pleasant. "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.10"
msgid "Lābhā vo, bhikkhave, suladdhaṃ vo, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "You’re fortunate, mendicants, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.11"
msgid "khaṇo vo paṭiladdho brahmacariyavāsāya. "
msgstr "to have the opportunity to live the spiritual life. "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.12"
msgid "Diṭṭhā mayā, bhikkhave, chaphassāyatanikā nāma saggā. "
msgstr "I’ve seen the heaven called ‘the six fields of contact’. "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.13"
msgid "Tattha yaṃ kiñci cakkhunā rūpaṃ passati iṭṭharūpaṃyeva passati, no aniṭṭharūpaṃ; kantarūpaṃyeva passati, no akantarūpaṃ; manāparūpaṃyeva passati, no amanāparūpaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "There, whatever sight you see with your eye is likable, not unlikable; desirable, not undesirable; pleasant, not unpleasant. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.14"
msgid "yaṃ kiñci jivhāya rasaṃ sāyati … pe … "
msgstr "Whatever sound … odor … flavor … touch … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.15"
msgid "yaṃ kiñci manasā dhammaṃ vijānāti iṭṭharūpaṃyeva vijānāti, no aniṭṭharūpaṃ; kantarūpaṃyeva vijānāti, no akantarūpaṃ; manāparūpaṃyeva vijānāti, no amanāparūpaṃ. "
msgstr "Whatever thought you know with your mind is likable, not unlikable; desirable, not undesirable; pleasant, not unpleasant. "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.16"
msgid "Lābhā vo, bhikkhave, suladdhaṃ vo, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "You’re fortunate, mendicants, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn35.135:1.17"
msgid "khaṇo vo paṭiladdho brahmacariyavāsāyā”ti. "
msgstr "to have the opportunity to live the spiritual life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.135:1.18"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

